(1543, 2, '2012-04-18 14:14:12', '2012-04-18 14:14:12', 'Four-time CTO. Technology experience from Intel and Toshiba. 18 years of experience with cloud computing, scalable network infrastructure, digital video systems, e-commerce, online transactions, messaging and web services. M.S. Electrical &amp; Computer Engineering from University of Arizona.', 'Bhavan Shah', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '892-revision', '', '', '2012-04-18 14:14:12', '2012-04-18 14:14:12', '', 892, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/892-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
