(113, 1, '2011-02-02 04:10:16', '2011-02-02 04:10:16', 'To get started, our new partners select from one of these templates for their basic website. Featuring plenty of ad banner slots, rotating local photos, event listings, editorial space and more, these templates are designed to serve you for months or years without any need for custom modification or expense. However, some of our partners enjoy creating their own custom look. Visit a few of our partners at the bottom of this page to see examples of what''s possible. AFTER we get you "soft launched" with one of the standard designs below, we''re happy to work with you to customize your website appearance however you like!\n<br />\n<br />\n<h3>MINIMALIST:</h3>\n<img class="imgBorder" src="/images/minimalTemplate-800.png" alt="" width="800" height="849" />\n<h3>GRAY:</h3>\n<img class="imgBorder" src="/images/silver-800.png" alt="" width="800" height="720" />\n<h3>BLUE:</h3>\n<img class="imgBorder" src="/images/blue-800.png" alt="" width="800" height="843" />\n<h3>RED:</h3>\n<img class="imgBorder" src="/images/red-800.png" alt="" width="800" height="843" />\n<h3>GREEN:</h3>\n<img class="imgBorder" src="/images/green-800.png" alt="" width="800" height="843" />', 'Color Options', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'color-options2', '', '', '2011-02-02 04:10:16', '2011-02-02 04:10:16', '', 0, 'http://www.townwizard.com/wp', 0, 'page', '', 0),
