(613, 2, '2012-03-28 15:05:57', '2012-03-28 15:05:57', '<div id="RightRail" class="nopad noborder">\r\n    <a class="advertiseLink"><br /><h5 class="redHead small">Contact Us for Advertising <img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_large.png" /></h5></a>\r\n    <a class="mediaKit" href="/wp-content/themes/5506/pdf/TownWizard_Media_Kit.pdf" target="_blank"><h5 class="redHead">Download Media Kit <img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_large.png" /></h5></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="leftContent advertise">\r\n<h3><span>Target the locals.</span>  Engage Customers Who Are On the Go Looking For Your Product &amp; Services Now</h3>\r\n<h3 class="nomarg"><span>The TownWizard Difference</span></h3>\r\n<h4>Local Content + Strong Network = Greater Engagement for Advertisers</h4>\r\n<div class="rule"></div>\r\n<div class="connect"><img alt="" width="500" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/advertise/tw_connect.jpg" /></div>\r\n<div class="head">Local Content</div>\r\n<p>Local knowledge plus local flavor create the most relevant and compelling content for consumers. Our partners are passionate entrepreneurs, community activists, and savvy promoters who are the center of their communities. They know what’s going on and they know what the locals want to do, see, eat, and drink. Our business is all about local content, local events, local restaurants, and local points of interest.</p>\r\n<div class="head">TownWizard Network</div>\r\n<p>TownWizard is a network of local partners who have created local guide apps &#038; websites in over 150+ locations worldwide with reach to consumers in 8 countries across 4 continents.</p>\r\n<p>We apply our knowledge of local audience and leverage our national footprint to connect consumers and businesses , making each interaction more engaging. Whether you a national advertiser looking to reach and engage a wide range of audience OR a local advertiser finding new ways to promote your business in your local community, TownWizard can fulfill your needs. We can place your ads on one, multiple, or all of TownWizard’s mobile guide apps and companion websites.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Interested in advertising?</strong> Please fill out <a class="advertiseLink">ad inquiry form here</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email us at <a href="mailto:advertise@townwizard.com">advertise@townwizard.com</a> or call us at 1-866-651-0001.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information on ad placements, see links below.</strong></p>\r\n<p class="nomarg"><strong>Ad Descriptions &amp; Specs</strong> (click links for more information):<br />\r\n<a href="/wp-content/themes/5506/pdf/TownWizard_Media_Kit.pdf" target="_blank">Website</a> - <span class="desc">We allow you to place listings, features, banners, coupons, promotions/contests on our local guides'' websites.</span><br />\r\n<a href="/wp-content/themes/5506/pdf/TownWizard_Media_Kit.pdf" target="_blank">Mobile Devices</a> - <span class="desc">We enable you to list news/events, post promotions/coupons/contest, place banner ads on our iPhone and Android apps.</span><br />\r\n<a href="/wp-content/themes/5506/pdf/TownWizard_Media_Kit.pdf" target="_blank">Social Media</a> - <span class="desc">We help you spread the word and improve your exposure to local customers via our local guides'' Facebook pages.</span><br />\r\n<a href="http://sms.townwizard.com/" target="_blank">SMS</a> - <span class="desc">We provide solutions for you to send messages and coupons directly to your customer''s cell phones!</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Advertise', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'advertise', '', '', '2013-08-06 01:59:24', '2013-08-06 01:59:24', '', 0, 'http://www.townwizard.com', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(616, 2, '2012-03-28 15:09:55', '2012-03-28 15:09:55', '<img class="devices" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/devices.png" alt="" />\r\n<h6><span>TownWizard Professional Solution offers everything</span> that you need to quickly launch your community’s first local guide app and website, including a custom iPhone app guide, a Google Android app guide, a complete website, a Content Management System (CMS), marketing support, press release and marketing collateral templates, sample ad sales guides, step-by-step video tutorials, and much more.</h6>\r\n<h6><span>Your new apps and website include these interactive features:</span></h6>\r\n<div class="rule"></div>\r\n<div id="RightRail" class="noborder">\r\n<div class="video"><iframe width="224" height="152" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/vuz-LHp9Lzg?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\r\n<p class="videoCaption">Watch this CNN Money video to learn more about TownWizard.</p>\r\n<div class="space"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="leftContent noborder">\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/features/events.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<h5>Local Event Listings</h5>\r\nYou can use your apps and website to promote concerts, festivals, charity fundraisers, art expos, live music listings, wine tastings, plays, civic meetings or any other local event. Locals and visitors alike want to know what’s happening in your area today, and YOUR new brand will become the definitive resource for this mobile information!\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/features/places.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<h5>Places</h5>\r\nLocals and visitors are always hungry for great restaurants. Your new mobile apps and website feature helpful details about your town’s best dining and nightlife options, including descriptions, maps, website links and more. Users can even use their smart phone’s built-in GPS capabilities to instantly find the restaurants and bars that are closest to their actual location!\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/features/news.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<h5>News &amp; Features</h5>\r\nYou can use this special section to promote local personalities, charities and businesses. Perhaps you’ll spotlight that Eagle Scout who just did a good deed. Or that friendly bartender who’s always ready with a smile and a joke. Or use it to highlight a favorite local charity. Use this feature to make local celebrities and to spotlight deserving individuals, businesses and organizations. This is where your editorial personality can really shine.\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/features/photos.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<h5>Photo and Video Gallery</h5>\r\nYou can also link to YouTube videos or upload fun videos about your community. Fans can view videos live, right on your website and app! Don’t worry: You don’t need to create the videos yourself… you can just share and promote great local videos that already exist!\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/features/weather.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<h5>Local Weather Reports</h5>\r\nYour smart phone apps feature detailed weather reports for your town, including severe weather alerts and extended forecasts. It’s all perfectly automated, so there’s no need to go out and hire your own meteorologist!\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/features/ad-banners.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<h5>Ad Banners</h5>\r\nYour website and your mobile apps feature built-in ad banners on all major pages. Mobile app ads can link to websites OR they can even dial a business phone number with a simple touch (i.e., "Touch here to call a taxi!"). We’ll provide you with sample ad sales kits and rate cards that are being successfully used by our other TownWizard partners, so that you can start selling ads whenever you’re ready.\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n<h5>Content Management System (CMS)</h5>\r\nThe Joomla Content Management System (the same CMS system used by such companies as Ebay, GE, McDonald’s, Sony, Pizza Hut, etc.) helps you manage all content on your mobile apps and website. Once you get the hang of it, entering a new restaurant or event takes less than 5 minutes. Once you enter a new listing, it’s instantly live on both the website and your mobile apps. Adding new videos and photos is easy too, once you learn the system. You don’t need to know any programming, and you don’t need to hire a web guy. The CMS makes it all easy, once you learn the basics. For more information about how Joomla works, visit www.joomla.org. It’s an open-source CMS that’s designed to grow with your business to any scale!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n<h5>Training</h5>\r\nOkay, so you''re not the most tech-savvy person on your block. No worries! Can''t figure something out? We''ve got a growing library of easy-to-follow online videos that walk you step-by-step through how to enter an event, how to add a new restaurant listing, how to create a business page on Facebook, how to market your new business, etc. Watch the videos right on your computer. Watch them as often as you like. We’re adding new videos all the time. It''s a fun and easy way to master your new business. We also have a Partner Mentoring program, where other TownWizard partners stand ready to help answer any questions that you have. We provide live orientation training and Q&amp;A sessions, led by experts.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n<h5>Distribution on app store &amp; Google Android Marketplace</h5>\r\nOnce you finish gathering and uploading all the content on your local guide, we will develop and launch your local guide in the TownWizard iPhone and Android app. Then it''s done, and you are officially in business. Anyone can download the TownWizard app for FREE and add it to their iPhone or Android. They can download it using their computer, or they can download it directly on their phone. (Did we mention that it’s a free download?)\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n<h5>Companion Website</h5>\r\nUm, so what exactly is a "Companion Website"? It''s a fully functional website that you also get as part of the deal. It features all of the same restaurant and event data, as well as the same exact photos, videos, etc. You even get to choose your own design. The website also has its own ad space that you can sell. To see examples of both websites and the apps, check out the examples tab above.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Professional Solution Features', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'features', '', '', '2013-09-19 00:25:48', '2013-09-19 00:25:48', '', 0, 'http://www.townwizard.com', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(618, 2, '2012-03-28 15:10:37', '2012-03-28 15:10:37', '', 'Press', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'press', '', '', '2012-03-28 15:10:37', '2012-03-28 15:10:37', '', 0, 'http://www.townwizard.com', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(642, 1, '2011-01-12 09:35:32', '2011-01-12 09:35:32', 'content here', 'Create Your Town&#039;s First Mobile Guide.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'create-your-towns-first-mobile-guide-2', '', '', '2011-01-12 09:35:32', '2011-01-12 09:35:32', '', 0, 'http://test.xhtmlchop.com/blog753/?p=33', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(792, 2, '2012-04-04 13:14:28', '2012-04-04 13:14:28', '<img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/devices_bussol.png" class="devices" />\r\n<h6>Whether you are a hotel, resort, tourism council, a chamber of commerce, special interest group, or just an individual looking to create your own brand of local guide for events/places, <span>our TownWizard software package includes everything</span> that you need to quickly launch a local guide, including a custom iPhone app, a Google Android app, a complete website, an Content Management System (CMS), step-by-step video tutorials, and more.</h6>\r\n<h6><span>Your new apps and website include these interactive features:</span></h6>\r\n<div class="rule"></div>\r\n<div id="RightRail" class="noborder">\r\n<div class="video"><iframe width="224" height="152" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/vuz-LHp9Lzg?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\r\n<div class="space"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="leftContent noborder">\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_2.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>Local Event Listings</h5>\r\n    You can use your apps and website to promote concerts, festivals, charity fundraisers, art expos, live music listings, wine tastings, plays, civic meetings or any other local event. Locals and visitors alike want to know what’s happening in your area today, and YOUR new brand will become the definitive resource for this mobile information!\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_3.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>Places</h5>\r\n    Locals and visitors are always hungry for great restaurants. Your new mobile apps and website feature helpful details about your town’s best dining and nightlife options, including descriptions, maps, website links and more. Users can even use their smart phone’s built-in GPS capabilities to instantly find the restaurants and bars that are closest to their actual location!\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_1.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>News &amp; Features</h5>\r\n    You can use this special section to promote local personalities, charities and businesses. Perhaps you’ll spotlight that Eagle Scout who just did a good deed. Or that friendly bartender who’s always ready with a smile and a joke. Or use it to highlight a favorite local charity. Use this feature to make local celebrities and to spotlight deserving individuals, businesses and organizations. This is where your editorial personality can really shine.\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_4.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>Photo and Video Gallery</h5>\r\n    You can also link to YouTube videos or upload fun videos about your community. Fans can view videos live, right on your website and app! Don’t worry: You don’t need to create the videos yourself… you can just share and promote great local videos that already exist!\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_5.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>Local Weather Reports</h5>\r\n    Your smart phone apps feature detailed weather reports for your town, including severe weather alerts and extended forecasts. It’s all perfectly automated, so there’s no need to go out and hire your own meteorologist!\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <h5>Ad Banners</h5>\r\n    Your website and your mobile apps feature built-in ad banners on all major pages. Mobile app ads can link to websites OR they can even dial a business phone number with a simple touch (i.e., “Touch here to call a taxi!”). You control (and keep) 100% of all revenue that you generate from your ads (and from every other revenue source that you can create, including e-commerce, retail, etc.).\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Content Management System (CMS)</h5>\r\n    The Joomla Content Management System (the same CMS system used by such companies as Ebay, GE, McDonald’s, Sony, Pizza Hut, etc.) helps you manage all content on your mobile apps and website. Once you get the hang of it, entering a new restaurant or event takes less than 5 minutes. Once you enter a new listing, it’s instantly live on both the website and your mobile apps. Adding new videos and photos is easy too, once you learn the system. You don’t need to know any programming, and you don’t need to hire a web guy. The CMS makes it all easy, once you learn the basics. For more information about how Joomla works, visit www.joomla.org. It’s an open-source CMS that’s designed to grow with your business to any scale!\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Tutorial Videos</h5>\r\n    Okay, so you’re not the most tech-savvy person on your block. No worries! Can’t figure something out? We’ve got a growing library of easy-to-follow online videos that walk you step-by-step through how to enter an event, how to add a new restaurant listing, how to create a business page on Facebook, how to market your new business, etc. Watch the videos right on your computer. Watch them as often as you like. We’re adding new videos all the time. It’s a fun and easy way to master your new business. We also have a Partner Mentoring program, where other TownWizard partners stand ready to help answer any questions that you have.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Distribution on <span>i</span>Tunes &amp; Google Android Marketplace</h5>\r\n    Once we finish developing your app, you will apply for an Apple Developer account. They approve it. Done. Once your app is approved, anyone can download it for FREE and add it to their iPhone or Android. They can download it using their computer, or they can download it directly on their phone.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Companion Website</h5>\r\n    Um, so what exactly is a “Companion Website”? It’s a fully functional website that you also get as part of the deal. It features all of the same restaurant and event data, as well as the same exact photos, videos, etc. You even get to choose your own design. The website also has its own ad space that you can sell. To see examples of both websites and the apps, check out the testimonials along the bottom side of this page. After we deliver your finished website, you can customize it in any way that you like.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Custom Options</h5>\r\n    All of the above features are included with your package. However, our team can also create special functionality for your app and website. For example, suppose you want to be able to sell things. Concert tickets. Gift certificates. T-shirts. Hotel reservations. We can build that for you, in your apps and on your new website. Or perhaps you want custom graphics. Simply contact us if you have any special requests or ideas, and we’ll get you a quote. It’s a whole lot easier (and more affordable) than you’d ever imagine!\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Corporate Solution', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'corporate-solution', '', '', '2013-09-01 17:18:48', '2013-09-01 17:18:48', '', 0, 'http://www.townwizard.com/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1507, 2, '2012-03-28 15:05:57', '2012-03-28 15:05:57', '<div id="RightRail" class="nopad">\n    <a class="advertiseLink"><br /><h5 class="redHead small">Contact Us for Advertising <img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_large.png" /></h5></a>\n    <a class="mediaKit" href="/wp-content/themes/5506/pdf/TownWizard_Media_Kit.pdf" target="_blank"><h5 class="redHead">Download Media Kit <img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_large.png" /></h5></a>\n</div>\n<div class="leftContent">\n<h3><span>Target the locals.</span>  Engage Customers Who Are On the Go Looking For Your Product &amp; Services Now</h3>\n<h3 class="nomarg"><span>The TownWizard Difference</span></h3>\n<h4>Local Content + Strong Network = Greater Engagement for Advertisers</h4>\n<div class="rule"></div>\n<div class="connect"><img alt="" width="500" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/advertise/tw_connect.jpg" /></div>\n<div class="head">Local Content</div>\n<p>Local knowledge plus local flavor create the most relevant and compelling content for consumers. Our partners are passionate entrepreneurs, community activists, and savvy promoters who are the center of their communities. They know what’s going on and they know what the locals want to do, see, eat, and drink. Our business is all about local content, local events, local restaurants, and local points of interest.</p>\n<div class="head">TownWizard Network</div>\n<p>TownWizard is a network of local partners who have created local guide apps &#038; websites in over 150+ locations worldwide with reach to consumers in 8 countries across 4 continents.</p>\n<p>We apply our knowledge of local audience and leverage our national footprint to connect consumers and businesses , making each interaction more engaging. Whether you a national advertiser looking to reach and engage a wide range of audience OR a local advertiser finding new ways to promote your business in your local community, TownWizard can fulfill your needs. We can place your ads on one, multiple, or all of TownWizard’s mobile guide apps and companion websites.</p>\n<p><strong>Interested in advertising?</strong> Please fill out <a class="advertiseLink">ad inquiry form here</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Email us at <a href="mailto:advertise@townwizard.com">advertise@townwizard.com</a> or call us at 1-866-651-0001.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>For more information on ad placements, see links below.</strong></p>\n<p class="nomarg"><strong>Ad Descriptions &amp; Specs</strong> (click links for more information):<br />\n<a href="/wp-content/themes/5506/pdf/TownWizard_Media_Kit.pdf" target="_blank">Website</a> - <span class="desc">We allow you to place listings, features, banners, coupons, promotions/contests on our local guides'' websites.</span><br />\n<a href="/wp-content/themes/5506/pdf/TownWizard_Media_Kit.pdf" target="_blank">Mobile Devices</a> - <span class="desc">We enable you to list news/events, post promotions/coupons/contest, place banner ads on our iPhone and Android apps.</span><br />\n<a href="/wp-content/themes/5506/pdf/TownWizard_Media_Kit.pdf" target="_blank">Social Media</a> - <span class="desc">We help you spread the word and improve your exposure to local customers via our local guides'' Facebook pages.</span><br />\n<a href="http://sms.townwizard.com/" target="_blank">SMS</a> - <span class="desc">We provide solutions for you to send messages and coupons directly to your customer''s cell phones!</span></p>\n</div>\n', 'Advertise', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '613-revision', '', '', '2012-03-28 15:05:57', '2012-03-28 15:05:57', '', 613, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/613-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(800, 2, '2012-04-04 14:24:08', '2012-04-04 14:24:08', '', 'Success Stories', '', 'draft', 'open', 'closed', '', 'success-stories', '', '', '2013-09-01 17:14:26', '2013-09-01 17:14:26', '', 0, 'http://www.townwizard.com/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(802, 2, '2012-04-04 14:26:59', '2012-04-04 14:26:59', '<div class="leftContent">\r\n\r\nFounded in 2010 in Florida with offices in New York, we are a leading global network of community guides and local mobile marketing platform. TownWizard enables entrepreneurs and organizations to create and monetize local guides that become the trusted mobile brands in their communities. We provide solutions that allow local businesses to reach local consumers.\r\n\r\nTownWizard is the definitive local events and what to do around town app that delivers authentic local knowledge of YOUR town &amp; YOUR community. Our free TownWizard iPhone and Android app allows users to access real-time interactive information on local events, restaurants, activities, services, news, photos &amp; videos across 100+ locations in 10+ countries and 6+ continents.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Company', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'company', '', '', '2013-08-06 01:42:52', '2013-08-06 01:42:52', '', 0, 'http://www.townwizard.com/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(804, 2, '2012-04-04 14:27:20', '2012-04-04 14:27:20', '<div class="leftContent">\r\n\r\nThe TownWizard Team is dedicated to delivering the most authentic and genuine information from local communities around the world to people on the go looking for things to do, places to visit, and services to use. TownWizard offers an exciting, fast-paced, work atmosphere and we are always looking for new talent to join our team.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in working for us, please send your resume to <a href="mailto:hr@townwizard.com">hr@townwizard.com</a>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Careers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'careers', '', '', '2013-08-06 01:44:07', '2013-08-06 01:44:07', '', 0, 'http://www.townwizard.com/', 0, 'page', '', 0),
