eceive an email containing a few "next steps."</li>\n	<li class="three">While you''re working on that stuff (a cool logo, URL, etc.), we''ll start setting your  new <a href="http://www.joomla.org" target="_blank">Joomla</a> CMS (Content Management System). After a few days, we''ll send you a link, along with your log-in info. Once you''re logged into the CMS, you can start entering local restaurants, events and photos. We provide you with online videos that show you how to do everything, step-by-step.</li>\n	<li class="four">We''ll also submit your new iPhone and Android apps for approval by Apple and Google. Getting official approval can take up to 2 - 3 weeks, which gives you plenty of time to work on fleshing out some really great local content.</li>\n	<li class="five">Once your app is approved, we''re ready to officially launch your new business. We even have press release templates ready for you! (and ad sales guides, to jump-start your revenue...)</li>\n	<li class="six">Now you can spend as much time as you like marketing your new mobile brand. Keeping up with local events and news is easy. We''ll teach you some tricks and tips so that you can stay on top of that stuff with just a few minutes every day. You''ll spend the rest of your time promoting your new business... on Facebook, Twitter, networking, through media trades, etc. Obviously, the more you put into it, the more you''ll get out. We''ve got a ton of ideas to share with you, as do our other TownWizard partners. We''re here to help support and grow your new business! So what are you waiting for? <a href="http://www.townwizard.com/sign-up">Get started now.</a></li>\n</ol>\n</div>', 'How It Works: 3 Steps For Creating Your Mobile Guide Business', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-revision-2', '', '', '2013-08-05 14:20:02', '2013-08-05 14:20:02', '', 30, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/30-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
