(1461, 8, '2013-09-27 00:26:25', '2013-09-27 00:26:25', '<div id="Steps">\n<div class="one box"><img alt="Step 1" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/how-it-works/step1.jpg" />\n<h4>1. Create Your Own Guide</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>We provide the technology</li>\n	<li>Choose your guide location</li>\n	<li>Update all the cool info, photos and videos about events, restaurants, services, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class="two box"><img alt="Step 2" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/how-it-works/step2.jpg" />\n<h4>2. Spread the Word</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Tell your friends and family about your guide apps and website</li>\n	<li>Then they tell everyone to download your free apps and visit your website</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class="three box"><img alt="Step 3" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/how-it-works/step3.jpg" />\n<h4>3. Earn Money</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Network with local businesses and organizations and let them know about advertising</li>\n	<li>Everyone will want to partner with the #1 mobile guide in your community, and you''ll earn money</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="noborder" id="RightRail">\n<div class="video"><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/vuz-LHp9Lzg?rel=0" height="152" width="224" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></div>\n<p class="videoCaption">Watch this CNN Money video to learn more about TownWizard.</p>\n\n<div class="space"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="leftContent">\n<div class="rule"></div>\n<iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/NSGYxgqI5DE?rel=0" height="360" width="640" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe>\n\n</div>\n<div class="cb"></div>', 'How It Works: <span>3 Steps For Creating Your Mobile Guide Business</span>', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-autosave', '', '', '2013-09-27 00:26:25', '2013-09-27 00:26:25', '', 30, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/30-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1462, 2, '2013-08-05 14:20:29', '2013-08-05 14:20:29', '<div id="Steps">\n<div class="one">We provide the technology; you select the town where you want to start your mobile guide app business and gather information..</div>\n<div class="two">You upload all the cool information about local events, restaurants, news, weather, activities, services, etc. to your local guide mobile app and website.</div>\n<div class="three">You tell your friends and family about your local guide mobile app and website, and they tell everyone they know about it. In no time, locals and visitors to your town will be downloading it.</div>\n<div class="four">You network with local businesses and organizations and let them know the opportunity to advertise and reach your local audience.</div>\n<div class="five">Everyone wants to get in on this, and you''ll make $$$ via advertising, sponsorships, coupon, e-commerce, etc.</div>\n</div>\n<div id="RightRail">\n<div class="video"><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/rllDw8TQf9Q?rel=0&amp;wmode=transparent" frameborder="0" width="224" height="152"></iframe></div>\n<div class="space"></div>\n<a class="contactLink">\n</a>\n<h5 class="redHead">Contact Us for Demo <img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_large.png" alt="" /></h5>\n<!-- a href="#" target="_blank">\n<h5 class="redHead">Download info in PDF <img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_large.png" /></h5>\n</a -->\n\n</div>\n<div class="leftContent">\n<div class="rule"></div>\n<h3>Get Started</h3>\n<ol>\n	<li class="one"><a href="http://www.townwizard.com/sign-up" target="_self">Sign-up here.</a> Once you''re registered, we charge you a one-time set-up fee of $795 ($2,995 for business solution). Your first monthly fee of $249 ($299 for business solution) won''t be charged until 30 days later. There''s no contract or obligation, only a software license agreement, so you can cancel at any time.</li>\n	<li class="two">After you''ve signed up, you''ll receive an email containing a few "next steps."</li>\n	<li class="three">While you''re working on that stuff (a cool logo, URL, etc.), we''ll start setting your  new <a href="http://www.joomla.org" target="_blank">Joomla</a> CMS (Content Management System). After a few days, we''ll send you a link, along with your log-in info. Once you''re logged into the CMS, you can start entering local restaurants, events and photos. We provide you with online videos that show you how to do everything, step-by-step.</li>\n	<li class="four">We''ll also submit your new iPhone and Android apps for approval by Apple and Google. Getting official approval can take up to 2 - 3 weeks, which gives you plenty of time to work on fleshing out some really great local content.</li>\n	<li class="five">Once your app is approved, we''re ready to officially launch your new business. We even have press release templates ready for you! (and ad sales guides, to jump-start your revenue...)</li>\n	<li class="six">Now you can spend as much time as you like marketing your new mobile brand. Keeping up with local events and news is easy. We''ll teach you some tricks and tips so that you can stay on top of that stuff with just a few minutes every day. You''ll spend the rest of your time promoting your new business... on Facebook, Twitter, networking, through media trades, etc. Obviously, the more you put into it, the more you''ll get out. We''ve got a ton of ideas to share with you, as do our other TownWizard partners. We''re here to help support and grow your new business! So what are you waiting for? <a href="http://www.townwizard.com/sign-up">Get started now.</a></li>\n</ol>\n</div>', 'How It Works: <span>3 Steps For Creating Your Mobile Guide Business</span>', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-revision-3', '', '', '2013-08-05 14:20:29', '2013-08-05 14:20:29', '', 30, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/30-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
