(1472, 2, '2013-08-05 15:05:56', '2013-08-05 15:05:56', '<div id="Steps">\r\n<div class="one box">\r\n<img alt="Step 1" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/how-it-works/step1.jpg" />\r\n<h4>1. Create Your Own Guide</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We provide the technology</li>\r\n<li>Choose your guide location</li>\r\n<li>Update all the cool info, photos and videos about events, restaurants, services, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="two box">\r\n<img alt="Step 2" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/how-it-works/step2.jpg" />\r\n<h4>2. Spread the Word</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Tell your friends and family about your guide apps and website</li>\r\n<li>Then they tell everyone downloading your apps and visiting your website</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="three box">\r\n<img alt="Step 3" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/how-it-works/step3.jpg" />\r\n<h4>3. Earn Money</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Network with local businesses and organizations and let them know about advertising</li>\r\n<li>Everyone will want to partner with the #1 mobile guide in your community, and you''ll earn money</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="RightRail" class="noborder">\r\n<div class="video"><iframe width="224" height="152" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/vuz-LHp9Lzg?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\r\n<div class="space"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="leftContent">\r\n<div class="rule"></div>\r\n<h3>Get Started</h3>\r\n<div class="getStarted">&ndash; sign up</div>\r\n<div class="getStarted">&ndash; onboarding</div>\r\n<div class="getStarted">&ndash; launch</div>\r\n<div class="getStarted">&ndash; promote &amp; sell</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>', 'How It Works: <span>3 Steps For Creating Your Mobile Guide Business</span>', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-revision-13', '', '', '2013-08-05 15:05:56', '2013-08-05 15:05:56', '', 30, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/30-revision-13/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1473, 2, '2011-01-12 09:23:34', '2011-01-12 09:23:34', '<img class="fltrt" src="/images/slide2img.png" alt="" />\n\nOur TownWizard software package includes everything that you need to quickly launch your town''s first mobile guide, including a custom iPhone app guide, a Google Android app guide, a complete website, an Content Management System (CMS), marketing support, press release and marketing collateral templates, sample ad sales guides, step-by-step video tutorials, and much more. Your new apps and website include these interactive features:\n<h3>Local Event Listings</h3>\nYou can use your apps and website to promote concerts, festivals, charity fundraisers, art expos, live music listings, wine tastings, plays, civic meetings or any other local event. Locals and visitors alike want to know what''s happening in your area today, and YOUR new brand will become the definitive resource for this mobile information!\n<h3>Restaurants &amp; Nightlife</h3>\nLocals and visitors are always hungry for great restaurants. Your new mobile apps and website feature helpful details about your town''s best dining and nightlife options, including descriptions, maps, website links and more. Users can even use their smart phone''s built-in GPS capabilities to instantly find the restaurants and bars that are closest to their actual location!\n<h3>News &amp; Features</h3>\n<img class="fltrt" src="/images/mobilimg3.png" alt="" />\n\nYou can use this special section to promote local personalities, charities and businesses. Perhaps you''ll spotlight that Eagle Scout who just did a good deed. Or that friendly bartender who''s always ready with a smile and a joke. Or use it to highlight a favorite local charity. Use this feature to make local celebrities and to spotlight deserving individuals, businesses and organizations. This is where your editorial personality can really shine.\n<h3>Photo Gallery</h3>\nHere you can feature fun photos of your town and locals, whether it''s showcasing images of local landmarks and attractions, or live images captured during area festivals, concerts and events. Your fans can even share real-time snapshots from their mobile phone! This is the future of local news delivery, and your new business will be on the cutting edge.\n<h3>Video Gallery</h3>\nYou can also link to YouTube videos or upload fun videos about your community. Fans can view videos live, right on your website and app! Don''t worry: You don''t need to create the videos yourself... you can just share and promote great local videos that already exist!\n<h3>Local Weather Reports</h3>\nYour smart phone apps feature detailed weather reports for your town, including severe weather alerts and extended forecasts. It''s all perfectly automated, so there''s no need to go out and hire your own meteorologist.\n<h3>Ad Banners</h3>\nYour website and your mobile apps feature built-in ad banners on all major pages. Mobile app ads can link to websites OR they can even dial a business phone number with a simple touch (i.e., "Touch here to call a taxi!"). We''ll provide you with sample ad sales kits and rate cards that are being successfully used by our other TownWizard partners, so that you can start selling ads whenever you''re ready. You control (and keep) 100% of all revenue that you generate from your ads (and from every other revenue source that you can create, including e-commerce, retail, etc.).\n<h3>Content Management System (CMS)</h3>\nThe <em>Joomla</em> Content Management System (the same CMS system used by such companies as Ebay, GE, McDonald''s, Sony, Pizza Hut, etc.) helps you manage all content on your mobile apps and website. Once you get the hang of it, entering a new restaurant or event takes less than 5 minutes. Once you enter a new listing, it''s instantly live on both the website and your mobile apps. Adding new videos and photos is easy too, once you learn the system. You don''t need to know any programming, and you don''t need to hire a web guy. The CMS makes it all easy, once you learn the basics. For more information about how Joomla works, visit <a href="http://www.joomla.org">www.joomla.org</a>. It''s an open-source CMS that''s designed to grow with your business to any scale!\n<h3>Tutorial Videos</h3>\nOkay, so you''re not the most tech-savvy person on your block. No worries! Can''t figure something out? We''ve got a growing library of easy-to-follow online videos that walk you step-by-step through how to enter an event, how to add a new restaurant listing, how to create a business page on Facebook, how to market your new business, etc. Watch the videos right on your computer. Watch them as often as you like. We''re adding new videos all the time. It''s a fun and easy way to master your new business. We also have a Partner Mentoring program, where other TownWizard partners stand ready to help answer any questions that you have.\n<h3>Companion Website</h3>\n<img class="fltrt shadowImg" src="/images/tallylife-screenshot.jpg" alt="" />\n\nUm, so what exactly is a "Companion Website"? It''s a fully functional website that you also get as part of the deal. It features all of the same restaurant and event data, as well as the same exact photos, videos, etc. You even get to <a href="http://www.townwizard.com/color-options">choose your own design</a>. The website also has its own ad space that you can sell. To see examples of both websites and the apps, check out the testimonials along the bottom side of this page. After we deliver your finished website, you can customize it in any way that you like.\n<h3>Custom Options</h3>\nAll of the above features are included with your package. However, our team can also create special functionality for your app and website. For example, suppose you want to be able to sell things. Concert tickets. Gift certificates. T-shirts. Hotel reservations. We can build that for you, in your apps and on your new website. Or perhaps you want custom graphics. Simply contact us if you have any special requests or ideas, and we''ll get you a quote. It''s a whole lot easier (and more affordable) than you''d ever imagine!', 'Features', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision', '', '', '2011-01-12 09:23:34', '2011-01-12 09:23:34', '', 29, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/29-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1474, 2, '2013-08-05 19:33:31', '2013-08-05 19:33:31', '<img class="fltrt" src="/images/slide2img.png" alt="" />\r\n\r\nOur TownWizard software package includes everything that you need to quickly launch your town''s first mobile guide, including a custom iPhone app guide, a Google Android app guide, a complete website, an Content Management System (CMS), marketing support, press release and marketing collateral templates, sample ad sales guides, step-by-step video tutorials, and much more. Your new apps and website include these interactive features:\r\n<h3>Local Event Listings</h3>\r\nYou can use your apps and website to promote concerts, festivals, charity fundraisers, art expos, live music listings, wine tastings, plays, civic meetings or any other local event. Locals and visitors alike want to know what''s happening in your area today, and YOUR new brand will become the definitive resource for this mobile information!\r\n<h3>Restaurants &amp; Nightlife</h3>\r\nLocals and visitors are always hungry for great restaurants. Your new mobile apps and website feature helpful details about your town''s best dining and nightlife options, including descriptions, maps, website links and more. Users can even use their smart phone''s built-in GPS capabilities to instantly find the restaurants and bars that are closest to their actual location!\r\n<h3>News &amp; Features</h3>\r\n<img class="fltrt" src="/images/mobilimg3.png" alt="" />\r\n\r\nYou can use this special section to promote local personalities, charities and businesses. Perhaps you''ll spotlight that Eagle Scout who just did a good deed. Or that friendly bartender who''s always ready with a smile and a joke. Or use it to highlight a favorite local charity. Use this feature to make local celebrities and to spotlight deserving individuals, businesses and organizations. This is where your editorial personality can really shine.\r\n<h3>Photo Gallery</h3>\r\nHere you can feature fun photos of your town and locals, whether it''s showcasing images of local landmarks and attractions, or live images captured during area festivals, concerts and events. Your fans can even share real-time snapshots from their mobile phone! This is the future of local news delivery, and your new business will be on the cutting edge.\r\n<h3>Video Gallery</h3>\r\nYou can also link to YouTube videos or upload fun videos about your community. Fans can view videos live, right on your website and app! Don''t worry: You don''t need to create the videos yourself... you can just share and promote great local videos that already exist!\r\n<h3>Local Weather Reports</h3>\r\nYour smart phone apps feature detailed weather reports for your town, including severe weather alerts and extended forecasts. It''s all perfectly automated, so there''s no need to go out and hire your own meteorologist.\r\n<h3>Ad Banners</h3>\r\nYour website and your mobile apps feature built-in ad banners on all major pages. Mobile app ads can link to websites OR they can even dial a business phone number with a simple touch (i.e., "Touch here to call a taxi!"). We''ll provide you with sample ad sales kits and rate cards that are being successfully used by our other TownWizard partners, so that you can start selling ads whenever you''re ready. You control (and keep) 100% of all revenue that you generate from your ads (and from every other revenue source that you can create, including e-commerce, retail, etc.).\r\n<h3>Content Management System (CMS)</h3>\r\nThe <em>Joomla</em> Content Management System (the same CMS system used by such companies as Ebay, GE, McDonald''s, Sony, Pizza Hut, etc.) helps you manage all content on your mobile apps and website. Once you get the hang of it, entering a new restaurant or event takes less than 5 minutes. Once you enter a new listing, it''s instantly live on both the website and your mobile apps. Adding new videos and photos is easy too, once you learn the system. You don''t need to know any programming, and you don''t need to hire a web guy. The CMS makes it all easy, once you learn the basics. For more information about how Joomla works, visit <a href="http://www.joomla.org">www.joomla.org</a>. It''s an open-source CMS that''s designed to grow with your business to any scale!\r\n<h3>Tutorial Videos</h3>\r\nOkay, so you''re not the most tech-savvy person on your block. No worries! Can''t figure something out? We''ve got a growing library of easy-to-follow online videos that walk you step-by-step through how to enter an event, how to add a new restaurant listing, how to create a business page on Facebook, how to market your new business, etc. Watch the videos right on your computer. Watch them as often as you like. We''re adding new videos all the time. It''s a fun and easy way to master your new business. We also have a Partner Mentoring program, where other TownWizard partners stand ready to help answer any questions that you have.\r\n<h3>Companion Website</h3>\r\n<img class="fltrt shadowImg" src="/images/tallylife-screenshot.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\nUm, so what exactly is a "Companion Website"? It''s a fully functional website that you also get as part of the deal. It features all of the same restaurant and event data, as well as the same exact photos, videos, etc. You even get to <a href="http://www.townwizard.com/color-options">choose your own design</a>. The website also has its own ad space that you can sell. To see examples of both websites and the apps, check out the testimonials along the bottom side of this page. After we deliver your finished website, you can customize it in any way that you like.\r\n<h3>Custom Options</h3>\r\nAll of the above features are included with your package. However, our team can also create special functionality for your app and website. For example, suppose you want to be able to sell things. Concert tickets. Gift certificates. T-shirts. Hotel reservations. We can build that for you, in your apps and on your new website. Or perhaps you want custom graphics. Simply contact us if you have any special requests or ideas, and we''ll get you a quote. It''s a whole lot easier (and more affordable) than you''d ever imagine!', 'Features', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-2', '', '', '2013-08-05 19:33:31', '2013-08-05 19:33:31', '', 29, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/29-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(1475, 2, '2012-03-28 15:09:55', '2012-03-28 15:09:55', '<img class="devices" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/devices.png" alt="" />\n<h6><span>TownWizard Professional Solution offers everything</span> that you need to quickly launch your community’s first local guide app and website, including a custom iPhone app guide, a Google Android app guide, a complete website, a Content Management System (CMS), marketing support, press release and marketing collateral templates, sample ad sales guides, step-by-step video tutorials, and much more.</h6>\n<h6><span>Your new apps and website include these interactive features:</span></h6>\n<div class="rule"></div>\n<div id="RightRail" class="noborder">\n<div class="video"><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/rllDw8TQf9Q?rel=0&amp;wmode=transparent" frameborder="0" width="224" height="152"></iframe></div>\n<div class="space"></div>\n<a class="space contactLink">\n</a>\n<h5 class="redHead">Contact Us for Demo <img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_large.png" alt="" /></h5>\n<div class="space"></div>\n&nbsp;\n<h5 class="redHead small">See TownWizard Guide Network <img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_large.png" alt="" /></h5>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n<div class="leftContent noborder">\n<div class="sect">\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/ds_2.jpg" alt="" /></div>\n<h5>Local Event Listings</h5>\nYou can use your apps and website to promote concerts, festivals, charity fundraisers, art expos, live music listings, wine tastings, plays, civic meetings or any other local event. Locals and visitors alike want to know what’s happening in your area today, and YOUR new brand will become the definitive resource for this mobile information!\n<div class="clear"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="sect shadow">\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/ds_3.jpg" alt="" /></div>\n<h5>Places</h5>\nLocals and visitors are always hungry for great restaurants. Your new mobile apps and website feature helpful details about your town’s best dining and nightlife options, including descriptions, maps, website links and more. Users can even use their smart phone’s built-in GPS capabilities to instantly find the restaurants and bars that are closest to their actual location!\n<div class="clear"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="sect shadow">\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/ds_1.jpg" alt="" /></div>\n<h5>News &amp; Features</h5>\nYou can use this special section to promote local personalities, charities and businesses. Perhaps you’ll spotlight that Eagle Scout who just did a good deed. Or that friendly bartender who’s always ready with a smile and a joke. Or use it to highlight a favorite local charity. Use this feature to make local celebrities and to spotlight deserving individuals, businesses and organizations. This is where your editorial personality can really shine.\n<div class="clear"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="sect shadow">\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/ds_5.jpg" alt="" /></div>\n<h5>Photo and Video Gallery</h5>\nYou can also link to YouTube videos or upload fun videos about your community. Fans can view videos live, right on your website and app! Don’t worry: You don’t need to create the videos yourself… you can just share and promote great local videos that already exist!\n<div class="clear"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="sect shadow">\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/ds_4.jpg" alt="" /></div>\n<h5>Local Weather Reports</h5>\nYour smart phone apps feature detailed weather reports for your town, including severe weather alerts and extended forecasts. It’s all perfectly automated, so there’s no need to go out and hire your own meteorologist!\n<div class="clear"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="sect shadow">\n<div class="image"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/ds_6.jpg" alt="" /></div>\n<h5>Ad Banners</h5>\nYour website and your mobile apps feature built-in ad banners on all major pages. Mobile app ads can link to websites OR they can even dial a business phone number with a simple touch (i.e., “Touch here to call a taxi!”). We’ll provide you with sample ad sales kits and rate cards that are being successfully used by our other TownWizard partners, so that you can start selling ads whenever you’re ready.\n<div class="clear"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="sect shadow">\n<h5>Content Management System (CMS)</h5>\nThe Joomla Content Management System (the same CMS system used by such companies as Ebay, GE, McDonald’s, Sony, Pizza Hut, etc.) helps you manage all content on your mobile apps and website. Once you get the hang of it, entering a new restaurant or event takes less than 5 minutes. Once you enter a new listing, it’s instantly live on both the website and your mobile apps. Adding new videos and photos is easy too, once you learn the system. You don’t need to know any programming, and you don’t need to hire a web guy. The CMS makes it all easy, once you learn the basics. For more information about how Joomla works, visit www.joomla.org. It’s an open-source CMS that’s designed to grow with your business to any scale!\n\n</div>\n<div class="sect">\n<h5>Tutorial Videos</h5>\nOkay, so you’re not the most tech-savvy person on your block. No worries! Can’t figure something out? We’ve got a growing library of easy-to-follow online videos that walk you step-by-step through how to enter an event, how to add a new restaurant listing, how to create a business page on Facebook, how to market your new business, etc. Watch the videos right on your computer. Watch them as often as you like. We’re adding new videos all the time. It’s a fun and easy way to master your new business. We also have a Partner Mentoring program, where other TownWizard partners stand ready to help answer any questions that you have.\n\n</div>\n<div class="sect">\n<h5>Distribution on <span>i</span>Tunes &amp; Google Android Marketplace</h5>\nOnce you finish gathering and uploading all the content on your local guide, we will develop and launch your local guide in the TownWizard iPhone and Android app. Then it''s done, and you are officially in business. Anyone can download the TownWizard app for FREE and add it to their iPhone or Android. They can download it using their computer, or they can download it directly on their phone. (Did we mention that it’s a free download?)\n\n</div>\n<div class="sect">\n<h5>Companion Website</h5>\nUm, so what exactly is a “Companion Website”? It’s a fully functional website that you also get as part of the deal. It features all of the same restaurant and event data, as well as the same exact photos, videos, etc. You even get to choose your own design. The website also has its own ad space that you can sell. To see examples of both websites and the apps, check out the testimonials along the bottom side of this page.\n\n</div>\n</div>', 'Professional Solution', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '616-revision', '', '', '2012-03-28 15:09:55', '2012-03-28 15:09:55', '', 616, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/616-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
