(1489, 2, '2013-08-05 20:32:23', '2013-08-05 20:32:23', '<div id="RightRail" class="noborder">\r\n<h5>Payment</h5>\r\n<div class="sect ctr">\r\nWe accept major credit cards and PayPal for international partners.\r\n<div>\r\n<img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/credit_card_logos.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="sect ctr">\r\n<img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/devices-small.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="leftContent">\r\n<h3>Launch your new mobile guide business for as low as $795.</h3>\r\n<h4>There''s no contract. You can quit at any time.</h4>\r\n<a href="/features"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/pricing-table.png" alt="" /></a>\r\n<div class="redLinks"><a href="/sign-up">Sign Up</a></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Pricing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1137-revision-7', '', '', '2013-08-05 20:32:23', '2013-08-05 20:32:23', '', 1137, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/1137-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1483, 2, '2011-01-12 09:23:54', '2011-01-12 09:23:54', '<div id="RightRail">\n<h5 class="redHead">Additional Info</h5>\n<div class="sect"><a href="http://www.townwizard.com/professional-license-agreement/">&gt; Professional Solution License Agreement</a></div>\n<div class="sect"><a href="http://www.townwizard.com/business-license-agreement">&gt; Business Solution License Agreement</a></div>\n<div class="sect"><a href="/faq">&gt; Frequently Asked Questions</a></div>\n<h5 class="redHead">Payment</h5>\n<div class="sect ctr">\n\nWe accept major credit cards and PayPal for international partners.\n<div><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/credit_card_logos.jpg" alt="" /></div>\n</div>\n<a class="contactLink">\n</a>\n<h5 class="redHead">Contact Us for Demo <img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_large.png" alt="" /></h5>\n</div>\n<div class="leftContent">\n<h3>Launch your new mobile guide business for as low as $795.</h3>\n<h4>There''s no contract. You can quit at any time.</h4>\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/townwizard-pricing4.png" alt="" />\n<div class="redLinks"><a href="/sign-up">Sign Up</a><a class="contactLink">Contact Us <img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/white_arrow_small.png" alt="" /></a></div>\nYou could shell out tens of thousands of dollars and spend many, many months to develop your own mobile business platform from scratch (including an iPhone app, an Android app, a companion website, a back-end Content Management System, marketing collateral, press release templates, etc.), or simply license our software and have your new business up and running within just a few weeks! (Trust us, our way is much easier…and much cheaper.) Whether you are joining the TownWizard network (Professional Solution) or starting a guide for an organization or existing business (Business Solution), we provide the the fastest, easiest and most economic way for you to start a local mobile guide.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>THERE''S NO CONTRACT, just a software license service agreement. You can quit at any time.</strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWith TownWizard Professional Solution, there''s only an one-time license and setup fee of $795. That gets you up and running. It gets you a website, a Google Android app, inclusion in the TownWizard iPhone app, the Content Management System (CMS), online tutorial videos, marketing templates, support and more. Then, you simply pay a monthly fee of $249. The fee’s auto-drafted from your credit card or debit account each month. All hosting and maintenance fees are included. That’s it! Again, there’s no contract to sign. Quit at any time with 30 days notice.\n\nOnce you get it fully launched, you should spend about 1-2 hours a day on content, and the rest of your time telling the world about your new local mobile guide! As the first mobile guide to your area, the business opportunities are immense. Seriously, what other business can you start for an initial investment of less than $1,000? With just a few ads, you’ll more than cover your monthly fee. (Don’t worry, we’ll provide you with the ad guides being used by our other TownWizard partners, so that you’ll know what ad rates to charge, and how to market your new business.) In fact, some of our partners have sold enough ads in their first couple of months to pay for TWO YEARS of software service!\n\nIf you’ve ever wanted to start your own business, but have been waiting for the right opportunity, this is it. Opportunities don’t get any bigger than the extraordinary one presented by the evolution of mobile computing and you can own the premiere mobile brand for your area.\n\n</div>', 'Pricing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1137-revision', '', '', '2011-01-12 09:23:54', '2011-01-12 09:23:54', '', 1137, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/1137-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1490, 2, '2013-08-05 20:34:01', '2013-08-05 20:34:01', '<div id="RightRail" class="noborder">\r\n<h5>Payment</h5>\r\n<div class="sect ctr">\r\nWe accept major credit cards and PayPal for international partners.\r\n<div>\r\n<img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/credit_card_logos.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/devices-small.jpg" alt="" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="leftContent">\r\n<h3>Launch your new mobile guide business for as low as $795.</h3>\r\n<h4>There''s no contract. You can quit at any time.</h4>\r\n<a href="/features"><img src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/pricing-table.png" alt="" /></a>\r\n<div class="redLinks"><a href="/sign-up">Sign Up</a></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Pricing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1137-revision-8', '', '', '2013-08-05 20:34:01', '2013-08-05 20:34:01', '', 1137, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/1137-revision-8/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
