at third parties may unlawfully intercept or access transmissions or private communications over an unsecured transmission.</strong>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<strong>5. Your Privacy Choices</strong>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Opt-out</span>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nOur marketing email correspondence will include instructions on how to unsubscribe from our marketing emails. Please follow the instructions in the emails to opt-out of an email. We will unsubscribe you from that newsletter or other programs within thirty business days.</div>\r\n<div class="leftContent">You can always contact us at privacy@townwizard.com in order to change your preferences with respect to marketing contacts.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Updating your personal information and contacting TownWizard</strong></span>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nYou can modify, add, or delete certain personal information by contacting us at privacy@townwizard.com. Even after you remove information from your profile or delete your account, copies of that information may remain viewable elsewhere to the extent it has been made generally available or shared with others, or it was copied or stored by other users once you made the information publicly available. We may also retain copies of your information in our archives. However, your name will no longer be associated with that information on the Website. If you have given third party applications or websites access to your information, they may retain your information to the extent permitted under their terms of service or privacy policies. But they will no longer be able to access the information through our Website after you disconnect from them.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<strong>6. Children''s policy</strong>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nWe are committed to protecting the privacy of children. We do not collect personally identifiable information from any person we actually know is under the age of 18. If we learn that we have collected personal information from a person under age 18, we will delete that information as quickly as possible. If you believe that we might have any information from a person under age 18, please contact us through the contact us information provided in the Website.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<strong>7. Social Media and Online Engagement</strong>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nWe use a variety of new technologies and social media options to communicate and interact with consumers. These sites and applications include popular social networking and media sites, online communities and more. To better engage the public in ongoing dialog, we use, or in the future may use, several third-party platforms including, but not limited to, Facebook, Twitter, and YouTube. These third party platforms are Web-based technologies that are not operated or controlled by us. Your use of such platforms is subject to the privacy policies of such platforms and is not covered by this Privacy Policy, and we encourage you to review the privacy policy of any company or website before submitting your Personal Information.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<strong>8. U.S. Governing Law.</strong>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nThe Website is designed and targeted to U.S. audiences and is governed by and operated in accordance with the laws of the U.S. We make no representation that this Website is operated in accordance with the laws or regulations of, or governed by, other nations.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nIf you are located in the European Union or elsewhere outside of the U.S., you do so at your own risk and initiative and you, not us, are responsible for compliance with any applicable local and national laws.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<strong>9. Changes to this Privacy Policy</strong>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nWe may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. When we post changes to this Privacy Policy, we will also revise the “Last Updated” date at the end of this Privacy Policy. If there are material changes to this Privacy Policy, we will notify you by email, or by means of a notice on our home page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to be informed of how we are using your information and to be aware of any changes to the Privacy Policy. Your continued use of the site after the posting of any amended Privacy Policy shall constitute your agreement to be bound by any such changes. Any changes to this Privacy Policy are effective immediately after being posted by us.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<strong>10. Notice for California Users</strong>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nUnder California’s “Shine the Light” law, California residents have the right to request in writing from businesses with whom they have an established business relationship (1) a list of the categories of personal information, such as name, address, e-mail address, and the type of services provided to that customer, that a business has disclosed to third parties (including affiliates that are separate legal entities) during the immediately preceding calendar year for the third parties’ direct marketing purposes, and (2) the names and addresses of all such third parties. To request the above information, please email us at privacy@townwizard.com or write to us at:\r\n<br /><br />\r\nPrivacy Officer<br />\r\nTownWizard, LLC<br />\r\n2 Overhill Road<br />\r\nSuite 400<br />\r\nScarsdale, NY 10583\r\n<br /><br />\r\nWe will respond to such written requests within 30 days following receipt at the mailing address above. We reserve the right not to respond to requests submitted other than to the address specified above or otherwise exempted by law. Please note that we are required only to respond to each customer once per calendar year.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<strong>11. Questions</strong>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nIf you have any questions about our privacy policy, you can contact our privacy officer at:\r\n<br /><br />\r\nprivacy@townwizard.com; or<br />\r\nTownWizard, LLC<br />\r\n2 Overhill Road<br />\r\nSuite 400<br />\r\nScarsdale, NY 10583\r\n<br /><br />\r\nTownWizard, LLC Privacy Policy last updated July 29, 2013.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1513-revision-6', '', '', '2013-08-10 15:20:55', '2013-08-10 15:20:55', '', 1513, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/1513-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1523, 2, '2012-04-04 14:24:08', '2012-04-04 14:24:08', '', 'Success Stories', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '800-revision', '', '', '2012-04-04 14:24:08', '2012-04-04 14:24:08', '', 800, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/800-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1524, 2, '2013-08-06 01:54:13', '2013-08-06 01:54:13', '<img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/devices_bussol.png" class="devices" />\r\n<h6>Whether you are a hotel, resort, tourism council, a chamber of commerce, special interest group, or just an individual looking to create your own brand of local guide for events/places, <span>our TownWizard software package includes everything</span> that you need to quickly launch a local guide, including a custom iPhone app, a Google Android app, a complete website, an Content Management System (CMS), step-by-step video tutorials, and more.</h6>\r\n<h6><span>Your new apps and website include these interactive features:</span></h6>\r\n<div class="rule"></div>\r\n<div id="RightRail" class="noborder">\r\n<div class="video"><iframe width="224" height="152" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/vuz-LHp9Lzg?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\r\n<div class="space"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="leftContent noborder">\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_2.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>Local Event Listings</h5>\r\n    You can use your apps and website to promote concerts, festivals, charity fundraisers, art expos, live music listings, wine tastings, plays, civic meetings or any other local event. Locals and visitors alike want to know what’s happening in your area today, and YOUR new brand will become the definitive resource for this mobile information!\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_3.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>Places</h5>\r\n    Locals and visitors are always hungry for great restaurants. Your new mobile apps and website feature helpful details about your town’s best dining and nightlife options, including descriptions, maps, website links and more. Users can even use their smart phone’s built-in GPS capabilities to instantly find the restaurants and bars that are closest to their actual location!\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_1.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>News &amp; Features</h5>\r\n    You can use this special section to promote local personalities, charities and businesses. Perhaps you’ll spotlight that Eagle Scout who just did a good deed. Or that friendly bartender who’s always ready with a smile and a joke. Or use it to highlight a favorite local charity. Use this feature to make local celebrities and to spotlight deserving individuals, businesses and organizations. This is where your editorial personality can really shine.\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_4.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>Photo and Video Gallery</h5>\r\n    You can also link to YouTube videos or upload fun videos about your community. Fans can view videos live, right on your website and app! Don’t worry: You don’t need to create the videos yourself… you can just share and promote great local videos that already exist!\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <div class="image"><img alt="" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2012/products/sd_5.jpg" /></div>\r\n    <h5>Local Weather Reports</h5>\r\n    Your smart phone apps feature detailed weather reports for your town, including severe weather alerts and extended forecasts. It’s all perfectly automated, so there’s no need to go out and hire your own meteorologist!\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect shadow">\r\n    <h5>Ad Banners</h5>\r\n    Your website and your mobile apps feature built-in ad banners on all major pages. Mobile app ads can link to websites OR they can even dial a business phone number with a simple touch (i.e., “Touch here to call a taxi!”). You control (and keep) 100% of all revenue that you generate from your ads (and from every other revenue source that you can create, including e-commerce, retail, etc.).\r\n    <div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Content Management System (CMS)</h5>\r\n    The Joomla Content Management System (the same CMS system used by such companies as Ebay, GE, McDonald’s, Sony, Pizza Hut, etc.) helps you manage all content on your mobile apps and website. Once you get the hang of it, entering a new restaurant or event takes less than 5 minutes. Once you enter a new listing, it’s instantly live on both the website and your mobile apps. Adding new videos and photos is easy too, once you learn the system. You don’t need to know any programming, and you don’t need to hire a web guy. The CMS makes it all easy, once you learn the basics. For more information about how Joomla works, visit www.joomla.org. It’s an open-source CMS that’s designed to grow with your business to any scale!\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Tutorial Videos</h5>\r\n    Okay, so you’re not the most tech-savvy person on your block. No worries! Can’t figure something out? We’ve got a growing library of easy-to-follow online videos that walk you step-by-step through how to enter an event, how to add a new restaurant listing, how to create a business page on Facebook, how to market your new business, etc. Watch the videos right on your computer. Watch them as often as you like. We’re adding new videos all the time. It’s a fun and easy way to master your new business. We also have a Partner Mentoring program, where other TownWizard partners stand ready to help answer any questions that you have.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Distribution on <span>i</span>Tunes &amp; Google Android Marketplace</h5>\r\n    Once we finish developing your app, you will apply for an Apple Developer account. They approve it. Done. Once your app is approved, anyone can download it for FREE and add it to their iPhone or Android. They can download it using their computer, or they can download it directly on their phone.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Companion Website</h5>\r\n    Um, so what exactly is a “Companion Website”? It’s a fully functional website that you also get as part of the deal. It features all of the same restaurant and event data, as well as the same exact photos, videos, etc. You even get to choose your own design. The website also has its own ad space that you can sell. To see examples of both websites and the apps, check out the testimonials along the bottom side of this page. After we deliver your finished website, you can customize it in any way that you like.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sect">\r\n    <h5>Custom Options</h5>\r\n    All of the above features are included with your package. However, our team can also create special functionality for your app and website. For example, suppose you want to be able to sell things. Concert tickets. Gift certificates. T-shirts. Hotel reservations. We can build that for you, in your apps and on your new website. Or perhaps you want custom graphics. Simply contact us if you have any special requests or ideas, and we’ll get you a quote. It’s a whole lot easier (and more affordable) than you’d ever imagine!\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Corporate Solution', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '792-revision-3', '', '', '2013-08-06 01:54:13', '2013-08-06 01:54:13', '', 792, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/792-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1525, 2, '2013-08-05 15:06:58', '2013-08-05 15:06:58', '<div id="Steps">\r\n<div class="one box">\r\n<img alt="Step 1" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/how-it-works/step1.jpg" />\r\n<h4>1. Create Your Own Guide</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We provide the technology</li>\r\n<li>Choose your guide location</li>\r\n<li>Update all the cool info, photos and videos about events, restaurants, services, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="two box">\r\n<img alt="Step 2" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/how-it-works/step2.jpg" />\r\n<h4>2. Spread the Word</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Tell your friends and family about your guide apps and website</li>\r\n<li>Then they tell everyone downloading your apps and visiting your website</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="three box">\r\n<img alt="Step 3" src="/wp-content/themes/5506/images/2013/how-it-works/step3.jpg" />\r\n<h4>3. Earn Money</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Network with local businesses and organizations and let them know about advertising</li>\r\n<li>Everyone will want to partner with the #1 mobile guide in your community, and you''ll earn money</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="RightRail" class="noborder">\r\n<div class="video"><iframe width="224" height="152" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/vuz-LHp9Lzg?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\r\n<div class="space"></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="leftContent">\r\n<div class="rule"></div>\r\n<h3>Get Started</h3>\r\n<div class="getStarted">&ndash; sign up</div>\r\n<div class="getStarted">&ndash; onboarding</div>\r\n<div class="getStarted">&ndash; launch</div>\r\n<div class="getStarted">&ndash; promote &amp; sell</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cb"></div>', 'How It Works: <span>3 Steps For Creating Your Mobile Guide Business</span>', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-revision-14', '', '', '2013-08-05 15:06:58', '2013-08-05 15:06:58', '', 30, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/30-revision-14/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
