(1604, 1, '2013-09-09 22:18:01', '2013-09-09 22:18:01', '<table cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr align="top">\r\n<td>\r\n<h1><strong>PROFESSIONAL</strong></h1>\r\n<strong></strong>Your TownWizard software package and service includes:\r\n\r\n- Branded iPhone and Google Android apps for your town\r\n\r\n- Companion website\r\n\r\n- Domain registration and hosting\r\n\r\n- Content Management System (CMS)\r\n\r\n- Launch, marketing and ad sales support\r\n\r\n- Inclusion in the <a title="TownWizard iPhone App" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/townwizard/id507216232?mt=8&amp;uo=4" target="_blank">TownWizard iPhone App</a> and <a title="TownWizard Android App" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.townwizard.android" target="_blank">TownWizard Android App</a>\r\n<p title="license agreement for the professional edition">Are you looking to build a local brand and start a local guide business? This is the right solution for you. There’s a one-time license fee of $795. That gets you up and running. It gets you the website, an iPhone app, an Android app, a Content Management System (CMS) and support videos and materials. Then, you simply pay a monthly fee of $249. There is no contract, just a standard software <a href="http://www.townwizard.com/professional-license-agreement/">license agreement for TownWizard Professional Solution</a>, and you can quit at any time with 30 days notice. The fee’s auto-drafted from your credit card or debit account each month. That’s it!</p>\r\n\r\n<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[add_to_cart item="1"]</td>\r\n<td align="left"><img title="geotrust" src="http://www.townwizard.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/geotrust.png" alt="" width="100" height="22" align="left" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<h1><strong>BUSINESS</strong></h1>\r\n<strong></strong>Your TownWizard software package and service includes:\r\n\r\n- White label iPhone and Google Android apps\r\n\r\n- Companion website\r\n\r\n- Content Management System (CMS)\r\n\r\n- Option for customization at additional cost\r\n\r\nDoes your business need a mobile app solution and a companion website? This is the right solution for you. There’s a one-time license fee of $2,995. That gets your business up and running along with access to Content Management System (CMS), support videos, and training materials. Then, you simply pay a monthly fee of $299. There is no contract, just a standard software <a href="http://www.townwizard.com/business-license-agreement/">license agreement for TownWizard Business Solution</a>, and you can cancel at any time with 30 days notice. The fee’s auto-drafted from your credit card or debit account each month. That’s it!\r\n<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[add_to_cart item="2"]</td>\r\n<td align="left"><img title="geotrust" src="http://www.townwizard.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/geotrust.png" alt="" width="100" height="22" align="left" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Store', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '5-revision-2', '', '', '2013-09-09 22:18:01', '2013-09-09 22:18:01', '', 5, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/5-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
