(1607, 2, '2013-09-07 05:59:56', '2013-09-07 05:59:56', '"I use the TownWizard Platform because it is easy to use, I get apps right out of the box, and the partner community is great to work with.  I get to run my business the way I see fit, but I also have the support of other partners and staff at TownWizard."', 'Ketan Shah<br />Chicago, IL<br />Desi Events Chicago', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1586-revision-5', '', '', '2013-09-07 05:59:56', '2013-09-07 05:59:56', '', 1586, 'http://www.townwizarddev.com/1586-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
